casebody.data:
Wednesday, May 20, 1992

MERIT DOCKET

92-698. State v. Tarver.

Stark County, No. CA-8632. On motion for leave to file memorandum in support instanter, motion to strike, and motion to dismiss. Motions to strike and to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Holmes, Wright and H. Brown, JJ., concur. Sweeney, Douglas and Resnick, JJ., dissent and would grant the motion for leave.
